{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": "",
        "content": [
            "要跳过此剧情吗？"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "一直以来，\\n多谢您的照顾了……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "是吗。\\n这就是你的答案啊……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "是。一切都无所谓了。\\n训练也练不下去。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "那天的事一直在脑海中\\n挥之不去，我已经不明白\\n自己的目标到底是什么了……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "哈哈……\\n这就是我没有自知之明，\\n妄想自己能成为骑士的惩罚吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "师父，对不起。不……\\n我已经没有资格再喊师父了。\\n我要回故乡的教会去。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "德莱茨",
            "context": "是吗。那今后就作为祭司，\\n好好地生活下去吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "南格拉斯迪亚大陆边境\\n霍普的故乡",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "唉……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "（放弃当骑士后的几周……\\n回到老家、穿上祭司服、\\n布教传法、听人忏悔……）",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "（曾经那么厌恶、让人提不起劲的\\n乡村祭司……虽然还是提不起劲……\\n但却感觉那么祥和……）",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "感觉悠闲得不太真实。\\n飞翔的鸟儿愉快地叫着……\\n大乡下也不会出现魔兽。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "不久前还在前线手忙脚乱的，\\n目睹人们不断倒下。\\n那都像梦一样……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "少女",
            "context": "霍普哥哥！\\n你看，蝴蝶～",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "哦！？哇，真的呢。\\n是蝴蝶……这是怎么了？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "少女",
            "context": "因为你自从回来之后\\n就一直唉声叹气的。\\n我想让你打起精神，就带来了！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "少女",
            "context": "大人们总说\\n这是因为“梦碎了”……\\n你还好吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "“梦碎了”吗……\\n说得也没错就是了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "不过有点不准确吧。\\n因为我从一开始就怀抱着\\n不切实际的梦想啊。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "少女",
            "context": "？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "哈哈……说了些消极的话呢。\\n你别在意……咦？\\n好像……有人在说话……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "见习祭司",
            "context": "扎托拉斯地区\\n好像又出什么事了。\\n在说受灾情况之类的。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "主教",
            "context": "哎呀，又来了吗。\\n中央传来的事都那么吓人啊。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "主教",
            "context": "教会骑士怎么招都人手不足，\\n每天都从希尔海姆地区\\n拉圣骑士过去……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "见习祭司",
            "context": "诶……虽然不太懂，\\n但中央也真够呛的啊。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "希尔海姆地区……\\n是师父所在的地方。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "师父现在也一定在前线战斗吧。\\n他会不会有事啊。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "啊……已经不关我的事了。\\n那个人实力强大，\\n我何必自寻烦恼……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "可恶。\\n总觉得好烦躁……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "不行……根本静不下来。\\n一躺下就更严重了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "老家悠闲而又和平……\\n可为什么……\\n我会有这种感觉……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "不用再看到有人倒下！\\n也不用再经历深感无力的悲伤回忆！\\n已经不会再有痛苦的事了！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "为什么我还是会胡思乱想！\\n就算再怎么努力……\\n我也无能为力啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "为什么……我……我……\\n呜呜……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "魔兽",
            "context": "嘎嗷嗷嗷嗷嗷嗷！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "不要，好可怕啊！\\n谁来救救我！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "咦？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "真是的……小弟弟你怎么会在这里。\\n这一带可是魔兽的巢穴。\\n要是我没来，你可就死定了啊。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "我、我家的狗，迷路了。\\n我想救它……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "“想救”你的狗吗。\\n好吧……那就没办法了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "大叔……你不生气了吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "嗯。我那顽固的弟子\\n大概会说“已经晚了”这种话……\\n不过我也不讨厌这种家伙。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "小弟弟，你听好了。\\n“尝试过，办不到”和“不去尝试”\\n是不一样的。所以不要放弃啊。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "你的狗现在怎么样了，\\n我不知道。但是……\\n也能因为不知道就断定它没救了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "如果想要救它，那就去救。\\n不去尝试的话，\\n一切都不会发生。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "所以，如果想救它，\\n就不要欺骗自己的内心。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "勉强自己忍耐的话，\\n反而会让自己受伤。\\n懂了吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "唔、嗯。懂了……我们说好了！\\n“天翼骑士”大叔！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "刚、刚才那是……梦……\\n不……不对。\\n那是，我以前的回忆……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "是啊……\\n小时候的我根本没考虑\\n能不能拯救这种事。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "当时只是想着\\n“要救它！”、“想救它！”。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "可现在我却在骗自己。\\n倔强地相信着“也许救不了\\n所以没有意义”这种歪理……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "“尝试过，办不到”\\n和“不去尝试”是不一样的。\\n我“想要尝试”！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "所以——我必须行动起来！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "剑……太好了，还没生锈。\\n哈哈……真沉啊。\\n都怪我没有坚持训练吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "可是，我不想后悔。\\n再一次……助我一臂之力吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "扎托拉斯地区附近\\n山路",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "哈啊、哈啊、哈啊……\\n终于来到这一带了，但……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "好大的雨啊……\\n本来这里就受灾了……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "堆积成山的……尸体……\\n那么多人……没有一个幸存……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "事到如今\\n光靠我一个人也……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "哈哈……为什么呢。\\n明明怕得浑身颤抖，\\n脚却停不下来。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "因为，我的内心在呐喊——\\n“要救他们”、“想救他们”。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "我不想再欺骗自己了！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "所以……我这就来。师父！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}